The Highlights

Australia are overwhelming favourites against Bangladesh as the teams clash in a World Cup Super Eight game in Antigua on Saturday. The Aussies have met the Bangladeshis 12 times so far in ODIs, winning 11 of those encounters. Bangladeshs lone victory came in Cardiff on June 18, 2005, when they won by 5 wickets. The following are few highs and lows:

